RVU File Information Tables

Source: R/tables.R
link_tables.Rd

RVU File Information Tables

Usage

rvu_link_table(years)

rvu_zip_links(years)

Arguments

years

<int> RVU source file year

Value

<tibble> containing information about RVU source files
